title: Shambles Kitchen
typeOfFood: Lacto, International, Organic, Western, Juice bar, Delivery, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Bewarned that it advertises a lot of meatstuff. Hipster cafe with a few vegan possibilities such as soup-of-the-day, fresh juices and smoothies, fresh lemonade, pre-made vegetarian sandwiches (which may be able to be made vegan).
